},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"佢可以賴死唔走，<br />\n主要因為你地未夠絕情，<br />\n<br />\n如果係我，刪名，換鎖，安CCTV，<br />\n佢上一次黎報一次警，<br />\n爆鎖就報警送佢入獄<br />\n<br />\n佢自然唔會會賴死唔走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:49:17.000Z","msg":"師兄講得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係細佬唔夠薑 話哂都係屋企人 又驚佢癲起上黎一鑊熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以先話之前一路loop 關係時好時壞<br />\n宜家當透明 忍讓下 就可以大部分時間相安無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40b54bc07eec9958675f3768eb61020f8b1344d","tid":1166583,"uid":224871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"唔知你啦，我屋企都搞緊，諗辦法趕走條契弟。只怪你地唔夠狠心比人恰"},{"pid":"b2c98e622dbc5bc081d0cf8c4f9e134f39e83eab","tid":1166583,"uid":119375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c40b54bc07eec9958675f3768eb61020f8b1344d","tid":1166583,"uid":224871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"唔知你啦，我屋企都搞緊，諗辦法趕走條契弟。只怪你地唔夠狠心比人恰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"因為驚比佢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發窮惡嘅人最得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n絲屋企單野都係咁？要順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf3c69afe2ae546f4acf28de29e453bc9fda40d","tid":1166583,"uid":224871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2c98e622dbc5bc081d0cf8c4f9e134f39e83eab","tid":1166583,"uid":119375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c40b54bc07eec9958675f3768eb61020f8b1344d","tid":1166583,"uid":224871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"唔知你啦，我屋企都搞緊，諗辦法趕走條契弟。只怪你地唔夠狠心比人恰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"因為驚比佢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />發窮惡嘅人最得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n絲屋企單野都係咁？要順利